Description: Builds and installs pinned 'bcftools' and 'htslib' command-line
    tools, including packaged plugins such as liftover and score. Provides
    executable discovery, deterministic plugin environment configuration,
    version inspection, and structured process execution. Variant table,
    'DuckDB', 'DuckLake', Arrow, Parquet, and annotation APIs are intentionally
    owned by 'Rduckhts' rather than duplicated here.
