Imports: processx
SystemRequirements: GNU make, pkg-config, libcurl, libgsl, libdeflate, libbzip2, libzlib, libssl-dev (or other ssl library), liblzma, libsuitesparse-dev/libcholmod5 (optional for pgs plugin)
Suggests: tinytest
